grade your character based on your score at the end of the game. Even if you can't clear it in a single play, keep challenging it until you succeed.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165100/extras/b2a0a9a5c831ce4bfe9e4dd09b1b48b3.poster.avif?t=1742198970\" width=640 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165100/extras/b2a0a9a5c831ce4bfe9e4dd09b1b48b3.webm?t=1742198970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165100/extras/b2a0a9a5c831ce4bfe9e4dd09b1b48b3.mp4?t=1742198970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ride the rhythm to gain an advantage in the game </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music is always playing in the disco, and by pressing buttons in time with the rhythm, you can fill your Ult gauge. Once it's full, you can unleash a powerful Ult.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165100/extras/d28aece75316790e611e0925f67b8a71.poster.avif?t=1742198970\" width=640 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165100/extras/d28aece75316790e611e0925f67b8a71.webm?t=1742198970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165100/extras/d28aece75316790e611e0925f67b8a71.mp4?t=1742198970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Use anything at your disposal</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you defeat zombies, they may also drop items other than money. Use these items to further improve your chances in the game.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165100/extras/757f637279a8e0486d55f37dc7525d81.poster.avif?t=1742198970\" width=640 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165100/extras/757f637279a8e0486d55f37dc7525d81.webm?t=1742198970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165100/extras/757f637279a8e0486d55f37dc7525d81.mp4?t=1742198970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
